{"categories":["beauty-cosmetics","events","seasonal-promotion","earth-day"],"collections":"","description":"Celebrate International Women's Day with our elegantly designed email template. Perfect for beauty and personal care brands, this template features a stylish fashion-forward design in a charming pink color palette to honor every woman on March 8. Use it to announce your Women's Day sales and promotions, or to simply express appreciation for the incredible women in your life. This email template is not only suitable for Seasonal Promotions but also for special events, making it a versatile addition to your marketing tools. Plus, with its Earth Day friendly design, it's a great way to show your brand's commitment to sustainability. Make every woman feel special and empowered with this beautifully crafted email template.","short_description":"Celebrate International Women's Day with our elegant email template. Perfect for beauty and personal care brands, it features a stylish fashion design in a charming pink palette. Ideal for Women's Day sales, events, and Earth Day promotions. Empower every woman with this sustainable, versatile marketing tool.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/galina-grahovska.jpg","description":"I have gained experience and skills in communications and organization of the work while I was hired in E.Miroglio EAD. I’ve also got excellent French as I was living in France for a few years.\r\n\r\nAbout an year ago, I’ve started designing interfaces and that’s definitely what I was looking for my whole life. I’m using Adobe Photoshop to design websites, emails and mobile apps. I also create prototypes in InVision to make the whole process from the start to the finish much easier.","short_description":"","display_name":"Galina Grahovska","id":"galina-grahovska"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head>